MAIN_MESSAGE: There is a power cut affecting the WA6 postcode area of Frodsham. We had no advance warning of this and only became aware of it at 12:33am. Repairs are taking longer than expected because of ongoing fault investigations and repairs. Our team are now working to get your power back on as quickly and as safely as possible by 4:30am. We will update this message if this information changes. We apologise for the inconvenience and thank you for your patience. This message was updated at 2:41am on 19th January
